content: With gems hidden behind historic corners, vibrant art and nightlife, Tribeca is where you want to be in New York City - and so is The Frederick. Thoughtfully-designed, The Frederick Hotel mixes vintage styles - like Mid-Century Modern and Art Nouveau - with turn-of-the-century and minimalist accents for a look as eclectic as the hotel itself. Here intriguing people, artful cocktails, and luxurious accommodations mingle for an experience that can’t be found anywhere else.
